en":[]}]},{"id":"133","parent":"129","text":"NO FARMACOLOGICO","guid":"YDtL4dt0Tfm7obzDYXxlpQ","children":[{"id":"134","parent":"133","text":"Suspender o ajustar farmacos cronotropicos negativos","guid":"u1Uq37GlRxOLiTa8ST6Xew","children":[]},{"id":"135","parent":"133","text":"DEPRESCRIPCION → primer paso siempre en AM","guid":"o27C2nBCTpCBcFFukYoMsA","children":[]}]},{"id":"136","parent":"129","text":"FARMACOLOGICO (transitorio)","guid":"JOOg6RKyT5W_Avx3RYCXlg","children":[{"id":"137","parent":"136","text":"ALGORITMO BRADICARDIA ACLS si inestabilidad","guid":"J-PgOWIzQqqhSZFOGQOpCw","children":[]},{"id":"138","parent":"136","text":"1a linea: Atropina 0.5-1 mg IV (repetir hasta 3 mg)","guid":"p_gXtHRcSJiFj1HClW3pWg","children":[{"id":"139","parent":"138","text":"UTIL en bloqueo suprahisiano (nodal)","guid":"viavo2CXQiWeBtBodsi8Yw","children":[]},{"id":"140","parent":"138","text":"INUTIL en bloqueo infrahisiano","guid":"piT3bhGBSJypvjIybwp7xw","children":[]},{"id":"141","parent":"138","text":"Cuidado: puede precipitar glaucoma agudo","guid":"IUSKMuz-RsiTP45Inf3cQA","children":[]}]},{"id":"142","parent":"136","text":"2a linea: Isoproterenol 2-10 mcg/min si atropina inefectiva","guid":"BCKtfSRuRZiAiV3bPoEc5A","children":[{"id":"143","parent":"142","text":"Betaagonista no selectivo β1 + β2","guid":"fvxrcfd3TtWjz3Vf9-G0zQ","children":[]},{"id":"144","parent":"142","text":"Puede causar taquicardia e isquemia","guid":"X0r2F1H2QgmKoB9CcSzdhA","children":[]}]},{"id":"145","parent":"136","text":"3a linea: Dopamina 5-20 mcg/kg/min o Epinefrina 2-10 mcg/min","guid":"mM5nEB0BRnWuYWeGQErtqA","children":[]},{"id":"146","parent":"136","text":"Marcapasos transcutaneo → si inestabilidad a pesar de farmacos","guid":"PduBHbOCQ2ixV9PuEpLgeg","children":[]}]},{"id":"147","parent":"129","text":"MARCAPASOS DEFINITIVO (ESC 2021 + ACC/AHA 2024)","guid":"ZOHAwghLQu6LVLJ9XwFeNg","children":[{"id":"148","parent":"147","text":"Indicado en bradicardia sintomatica persistente","guid":"Ka0XdJYvRuefHKUqvhNTvQ","children":[]},{"id":"149","parent":"147","text":"Indicado en BAV avanzado o completo (independiente de sintomas en algunos casos)","guid":"PgJfR2UMSoaSmvfVcSaJGg","children":[]},{"id":"150","parent":"147","text":"Seleccion de dispositivo","guid":"vL8u_AjMS8mde0SkAGdknQ","children":[{"id":"151","parent":"150","text":"DDD (bicameral) → preferido en ritmo sinusal (preserva sincronia AV)","guid":"10XSmgp_Su6gO3wJL18deQ","children":[]},{"id":"152","parent":"150","text":"VVI (monocameral) → FA permanente con BAV","guid":"9iezVs0cSVe26bqgRig_-Q","children":[]},{"id":"153","parent":"150","text":"CRT → si FEVI <40% y necesidad de pacing frecuente","guid":"DuTHdChCRIKX5FJ0xG-ySA","children":[]},{"id":"154","parent":"150","text":"LBBAP (CSP) → alternativa fisiologica a estimulacion VD convencional","guid":"jpdI3R_zTz69dzxa5MLCsQ","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"155","parent":"0","text":"CONSIDERACIONES GERIATRICAS","guid":"LRDuS-v1TzO6EkKdjy8Mng","children":[{"id":"156","parent":"155","text":"↑ Prevalencia por deterioro nodo sinusal y fibrosis sistema de conduccion","guid":"RxQMWBSiT_iJrl8Ub32Z_A","children":[]},{"id":"157","parent":"155","text":"Presentacion ATIPICA en AM","guid":"3lyf4e6TQ6uU1iWDhnZaSw","children":[{"id":"158","parent":"157","text":"Caidas (bradicardia paroxistica sub-diagnosticada)","guid":"xtl9bDFERCaVQunqjwvXIg","children":[]},{"id":"159","parent":"157","text":"Deterioro cognitivo, confusion","guid":"JF4nGXNeSgaqOd6PJlGf-Q","children":[]},{"id":"160","parent":"157","text":"Sincope con caida → BAV completo en DD SIEMPRE","guid":"OhfWOrvdSaCf4ww8m4NGZw","children":[]}]},{"id":"161","parent":"155","text":"POLIFARMACIA → primer factor a evaluar","guid":"YK8P9mDISd-28J1ZKefhtA","children":[{"id":"162","parent":"161","text":"↑ Prevalencia efectos adversos por comorbilidad","guid":"pfPoKGWoSSujfqutg6plkA","children":[]},{"id":"163","parent":"161","text":"↓ Funcion renal y hepatica → acumulacion de farmacos","guid":"_6CkylttSC-VPlQwsN2vqA","children":[]},{"id":"164","parent":"161","text":"STOPP criteria: betabloqueadores en bradicardia <50 lpm","guid":"f75FWnpuQfy4JP5ak5tQHw","children":[]},{"id":"165","parent":"161","text":"DEPRESCRIBIR antes de considerar marcapasos","guid":"_flVU4xSTxmdX0ukF7ZonA","children":[]}]},{"id":"166","parent":"155","text":"Mayor impacto hemodinamico por menor reserva cardiovascular","guid":"U4Uz84K7S92lJv2dQJdd3g","children":[]},{"id":"167","parent":"155","text":"Riesgo de delirium post-implante MCP → prevencion multicomponente","guid":"S6SELnzwRO6-EIX5_P5NKg","children":[]},{"id":"168","parent":"155","text":"Evaluacion de fragilidad (CFS) antes de decision terapeutica","guid":"2ZrQBKyGQyqVxf8VmC4rHQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"169","parent":"0","text":"VER TAMBIEN","guid":"9hI_16QVQgqf0zNIGbI-qg","children":[{"id":"170","parent":"169","text":"→ Bloqueo AV Completo (Cardiologia)","guid":"6POHgZ5GRhmHcL4VIx-r-g","children":[]},{"id":"171","parent":"169","text":"→ Sincope (Cardiologia)","guid":"nrU1DRGZRgSZty9R4b7Ydg","children":[]},{"id":"172","parent":"169","text":"→ Farmacologia cardiovascular (Farmacologia)","guid":"H92CZeGwTxqylGKgPmEwxg","children":[]},{"id":"173","parent":"169","text":"→ Deprescripcion (Farmacologia)","guid":"dr3eRKQMTkyjHayrKGqs7g","children":[]},{"id":"174","parent":"169","text":"→ Envejecimiento cardiovascular (Cardiogeriatria)","guid":"aRb5Qf6lRsiDUXkyLPUk2Q","children":[]},{"id":"175","parent":"169","text":"→ Fragilidad y CFS (Valoracion Geriatrica)","guid":"4lgJOFVOTvKKa6MIZQgvKg","children":[]}]},{"id":"176","parent":"0","text":"PERLAS CLINICAS","guid":"TEkw0vF_SEypzlkrWIKv3w","children":[{"id":"177","parent":"176","text":"Mobitz II → siempre indica bloqueo infranodal → indicacion de MCP independiente de sintomas","guid":"cgITj-OBRtKs__Nb7Rif8Q","children":[]},{"id":"178","parent":"176","text":"Bradicardia por farmacos → SIEMPRE deprescribir ANTES de indicar MCP","guid":"yf6ELXQ5RraXdQE9fqHeRQ","children":[]},{"id":"179","parent":"176","text":"FC <40 lpm + QRS ancho → no esperar sintomas para actuar (alto riesgo asistolia)","guid":"QaagO2wcSeGs63A6gfe6tQ","children":[]},{"id":"180","parent":"176","text":"Donepezilo → causa subdiagnosticada de bradicardia en AM con demencia","guid":"GsNmfKhsSICozbYmA5wwwQ","children":[]},{"id":"181","parent":"176","text":"SAHOS → causa tratable de bradicardia nocturna; CPAP puede resolverla","guid":"Jn-0R-fQQym82ZgnPxwBvg","children":[]},{"id":"182","parent":"176","text":"Holter nocturno en AM con caidas → descartar BAV paroxistico","guid":"VrhBDr6aSBatkNObmzFWXQ","children":[]},{"id":"183","parent":"176","text":"Atropina CONTRAINDICADA en BAV infranodal (QRS ancho) → puede accelerar escape y colapsar","guid":"6RhzfcxeQACeqrQYHGrGEA","children":[]},{"id":"184","parent":"176","text":"Sincope en AM + caida → NO asumir causa mecanica: siempre ECG y Holter","guid":"AHTRjzWaTEurSBJQamxBJg","children":[]},{"id":"185","parent":"176","text":"Chagas en adulto joven latinoamericano con BAV → etiologia a considerar siempre","guid":"K3BeGr14SqyhldEyggPZlA","children":[]},{"id":"186","parent":"176","text":"REFERENCIAS","guid":"L_jBnIBBSgCUHOMlSZvbbg","children":[{"id":"187","parent":"186","text":"1. Glikson M, et al. 2021 ESC Guidelines on cardiac pacing and CRT. Eur Heart J. 2021;42(35):3427-3520.","guid":"_NnN0xyBRei6gRDqVF8YFw","children":[]},{"id":"188","parent":"186","text":"2. Kusumoto FM, et al. 2018 ACC/AHA/HRS Guideline on Bradycardia. J Am Coll Cardiol. 2019;74(7):e51-e156.","guid":"Qr3o3lBFQNevPgESFsNi8g","children":[]},{"id":"189","parent":"186","text":"3. Ellenbogen KA, et al. 2024 ACC/AHA/ACPE/HRS Guideline on Cardiac Pacing and CRT. J Am Coll Cardiol. 2024;84(19):1935-2038.","guid":"KKbrILM1S2WUyvPwj3rZAQ","children":[]},{"id":"190","parent":"186","text":"4. Jensen PN, et al. Sick sinus syndrome in the general population. J Am Coll Cardiol. 2014;64(6):531-8.","guid":"w27MoEisSX2K45ALyuIpHg","children":[]},{"id":"191","parent":"186","text":"5. Mangrum JM, DiMarco JP. Evaluation and management of bradycardia. N Engl J Med. 2000;342(10):703-9.","guid":"MuIUq5ShR0i2kCprb3kSfQ","children":[]},{"id":"192","parent":"186","text":"6. Wenckebach KF. Zur Analyse des unregelmassigen Pulses. Z Klin Med. 1899;37:475-88.","guid":"VAbSkk0NTWm5CjFwWPO1fg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":192,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Estudios Pivotales","folder":"Estudios Pivotales","filename":"BAFTA 2007","id":"map_174","resolved_references":[]}